				                <div>Hello Gene,<br />
<br />
It looks like you need to change:<br />
<br />
&lt;pre class=&quot;code_block&quot; style=&quot;margin: -10px 0px -30px 0px; line-height: .9em&quot;&gt;include_once 'home/mediqxX/public_html/php/db_connect.php';&lt;/pre&gt;<br />
